## 🗄️ Database Model

```sql
-- Master item kondisi mesin (19 items)
pre_shift_checklist_items
  → id, category (MATERIAL/KONDISI_MESIN/KEAMANAN/MANPOWER)
  → item_code, item_name, sort_order, is_active

-- Mapping item ke mesin (mana yang applicable)
pre_shift_checklist_machine_items
  → id, item_id, machine_id, is_applicable (default true)

-- Submission per mesin per shift per hari
pre_shift_checklist_submissions
  → id, machine_id, tanggal, shift, operator_name
  → submitted_by, submitted_at, status (draft/submitted)

-- Jawaban per item
pre_shift_checklist_answers
  → id, submission_id, item_id
  → status (OK/NG/NA), catatan, photo_url
```

---

## 📁 API Endpoints

```
GET  /pre-shift-checklist/items                    - List semua item
GET  /pre-shift-checklist/machines/<id>/items      - Items untuk mesin tertentu
POST /pre-shift-checklist/submit                   - Submit checklist
GET  /pre-shift-checklist/submissions              - List submissions (filter by date/machine)
GET  /pre-shift-checklist/submissions/<id>         - Detail submission
GET  /pre-shift-checklist/status                   - Status hari ini per mesin
```

---

## 🖥️ UI Design

### Halaman Utama (/app/production/pre-shift-checklist)
- Grid mesin dengan status checklist hari ini (✅ Submitted / ⏳ Pending / ❌ Belum)
- Filter by tanggal
- Klik mesin → buka form checklist

### Form Checklist
- Header: Mesin, Tanggal, Shift, Nama Operator
- 4 Tab/Section:
  1. Kelengkapan Material (placeholder)
  2. Kondisi Mesin (19 item, sesuai mesin)
  3. Keamanan Mesin (placeholder)
  4. Man Power (8 item)
- Setiap item: Radio OK/NG/NA + field catatan
- Tombol Submit

